(1) The Minister shall have power to declare, by statutory notice, the width of any road or class or classes of road . Except as otherwise provided the width shall be— (a) for a main road , two hundred feet; (b) for a district road , one hundred and twenty feet; (c) for a branch road , one hundred and twenty feet; (d) for any other class of road , sixty feet.
